About Perez Hilton:
The original influencer, Perez Hilton founded and oversees one of the most iconic websites ever. In addition to his eponymous blog, he is the host of a very successful podcast, has a loyal following across two YouTube channels, has written three books, has acted in countless TV shows and films -  as well as the stage. And, most importantly, he is the proud father of three happy and thriving kid and an adult child, his mother. Perez is one of the most sought after commentators and your best friend!"
